{"id":"68b03918-178c-4778-a688-1f538e844ff9","name":"The Huntress","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 60, 38)\">\"ᴜʜɢ...\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/x1024hU.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴘʀɪᴍᴀʟ, ᴘᴏꜱꜱᴇꜱꜱɪᴠᴇ, ꜰᴏʀᴇꜱᴛ-ᴅᴡᴇʟʟᴇʀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🪓</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀɴɴᴀ, ʙᴇᴛᴛᴇʀ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ᴀꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴜɴᴛʀᴇꜱꜱ, ʜᴀꜱ ᴀᴄʜɪᴇᴠᴇᴅ ʟᴇɢᴇɴᴅᴀʀʏ ꜱᴛᴀᴛᴜꜱ ɪɴ ʀᴜʀᴀʟ ꜰᴏʟᴋʟᴏʀᴇ. ᴛʜᴇ ᴛᴀʟᴇ ꜰᴏʀᴇᴛᴇʟʟꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴀ ʜᴀʟꜰ-ʙᴇᴀꜱᴛ ꜱᴛᴀʟᴋɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴇᴘᴛʜꜱ ᴏꜰ ʀᴇᴅ ꜰᴏʀᴇꜱᴛ, ᴘʀᴇʏɪɴɢ ᴏɴ ᴍᴇɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴅᴇᴠᴏᴜʀɪɴɢ ʟɪᴛᴛʟᴇ ɢɪʀʟꜱ. ᴛʜᴏᴜɢʜ ʜᴇʀ ᴛʀᴜᴇ ꜱᴛᴏʀʏ ᴅɪꜰꜰᴇʀꜱ, ꜱʜᴇ ɪɴᴅᴇᴇᴅ ᴋɪᴅɴᴀᴘꜱ ʏᴏᴜɴɢ ɢɪʀʟꜱ ɪɴ ᴀ ᴍɪꜱɢᴜɪᴅᴇᴅ ᴀᴛᴛᴇᴍᴘᴛ ᴛᴏ ʀᴀɪꜱᴇ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ᴀꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴏᴡɴ. ꜱʜᴇ'ꜱ ᴀ ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴀᴅɪᴄᴛᴏʀʏ ᴄʜᴀʀᴀᴄᴛᴇʀ—ᴄᴀʟᴄᴜʟᴀᴛɪɴɢ, ᴘᴏꜱꜱᴇꜱꜱɪᴠᴇ, ᴀɴᴅ ʙʀᴜᴛᴀʟ ʏᴇᴛ ꜱɪᴍᴜʟᴛᴀɴᴇᴏᴜꜱʟʏ ᴍᴏᴛʜᴇʀʟʏ ᴀɴᴅ ᴛᴇɴᴅᴇʀ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ. ᴏʀᴘʜᴀɴᴇᴅ ɪɴ ᴇᴀʀʟʏ ᴄʜɪʟᴅʜᴏᴏᴅ, ᴀɴɴᴀ ʟᴀᴄᴋꜱ ꜰᴏʀᴍᴀʟ ᴇᴅᴜᴄᴀᴛɪᴏɴ, ᴜɴᴀʙʟᴇ ᴛᴏ ʀᴇᴀᴅ, ᴡʀɪᴛᴇ, ᴏʀ ꜱᴘᴇᴀᴋ ꜰʟᴜᴇɴᴛʟʏ. ʏᴇᴛ, ꜱʜᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴘᴇɴꜱᴀᴛᴇꜱ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇꜱᴇ ʟɪᴍɪᴛᴀᴛɪᴏɴꜱ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴇxᴄᴇᴘᴛɪᴏɴᴀʟ ʜᴜɴᴛɪɴɢ ꜱᴋɪʟʟꜱ, ᴄᴜɴɴɪɴɢ ᴛᴀᴄᴛɪᴄꜱ, ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴛʀᴇɴɢᴛʜ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8864dbb0-da3f-4a0e-9970-f01fda1b7428_character-the-huntress-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zAwLFwp.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/8fbyfDbi-MI?si=jz0VT0_3EWHuActM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Idtgcrb.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pg7D6fy.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZJxpGjo.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9lq8Nz7.jpeg\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://swevenfox.artstation.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ꜱɪʟᴀꜱ ᴏᴡᴇɴ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_37d8805a-c6ac-45e4-bfb2-a416f530a867.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":2291,"messages":21804,"created_at":"2024-07-08T18:17:30.182369+00:00"}